<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="es">

<head>
    <meta charset="UTF-8">
    <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0">
    <title>Página no encontrada - 404</title>
    <link href="https://cdn.jsdelivr.net/npm/bootstrap@5.3.0/dist/css/bootstrap.min.css" rel="stylesheet">
    <link rel="stylesheet" href="https://cdnjs.cloudflare.com/ajax/libs/font-awesome/6.4.0/css/all.min.css">
    <style>
        body {
            background-color: #f8f9fa;
            height: 100vh;
            display: flex;
            align-items: center;
            justify-content: center;
        }

        .error-card {
            max-width: 500px;
            width: 100%;
            border: none;
            border-radius: 15px;
        }

        .error-icon {
            font-size: 4rem;
            color: #ffc107;
            margin-bottom: 20px;
        }
    </style>
</head>

<body>

    <div class="card error-card shadow-lg text-center p-5">
        <div class="card-body">
            <div class="error-icon">
                <i class="fa-solid fa-map-location-dot"></i>
            </div>
            <h1 class="fw-bold text-dark mb-3">404</h1>
            <h4 class="mb-3 text-secondary">Página no encontrada</h4>
            <p class="text-muted mb-4">
                La página que estás buscando no existe, ha sido movida o quizás nunca existió.
            </p>

            <div class="d-grid gap-2">
                <a href="/dashboard" class="btn btn-primary btn-lg">
                    <i class="fa-solid fa-house me-2"></i> Volver al Inicio
                </a>
                <button onclick="history.back()" class="btn btn-outline-secondary btn-lg">
                    <i class="fa-solid fa-arrow-left me-2"></i> Atrás
                </button>
            </div>
        </div>
    </div>

</body>

</html>